解支持獨裁=無言論自由？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:44:55.000Z","msg":"當獨裁政權霸佔一個地區，嗰個地區嘅所有人都冇言論自由<br />\n所以要消滅獨裁政權，就要支持獨裁政權嘅賤種冇咗言論自由先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:51:23.000Z","msg":"Less well known is the paradox of tolerance: Unlimited tolerance must lead to the disappearance of tolerance. If we extend unlimited tolerance even to those who are intolerant, if we are not prepared to defend a tolerant society against the onslaught of the intolerant, then the tolerant will be destroyed, and tolerance with them. &mdash; In this formulation, I do not imply, for instance, that we should always suppress the utterance of intolerant philosophies; as long as we can counter them by rational argument and keep them in check by public opinion, suppression would certainly be unwise. But we should claim the right to suppress them if necessary even by force; for it may easily turn out that they are not prepared to meet us on the level of rational argument, but begin by denouncing all argument; they may forbid their followers to listen to rational argument, because it is deceptive, and teach them to answer arguments by the use of their fists or pistols. We should therefore claim, in the name of tolerance, the right not to tolerate the intolerant.<br />\n-Karl Popper"},{"pid":"1e904b533eab77fded5f4e9523a54edce88fe97a","tid":1180589,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0bd75b508dd96146303c4a915b164e3b6d0608e","tid":1180589,"uid":244332,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"044c8ec969b8fa346555bd050a538f7c143eabfd","tid":1180589,"uid":25073,"like":4,"dislike":18,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"77549939adda2c973a1e0d1ebd6111cff